Package: msaviewr
Title: Interactive Multiple Sequence Alignment Viewer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Colin", "Diesh", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "colin.diesh@gmail.com")
Description: Interactive viewer for multiple sequence alignments and
    phylogenetic trees, powered by react-msaview. Works with standard
    R/Bioconductor objects (phylo, DNAStringSet, AAStringSet,
    MultipleAlignment) and integrates with ggtree/treeio. Supports
    FASTA, Stockholm, Clustal, and Newick formats. Renders as an
    htmlwidget in RStudio, R Markdown, Quarto, and Shiny.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/GMOD/react-msaview
BugReports: https://github.com/GMOD/react-msaview/issues
Imports:
    htmlwidgets (>= 1.5.0)
Suggests:
    ape,
    treeio,
    Biostrings,
    ggtree,
    shiny,
    knitr,
